50|$|The river {{has been}} {{polluted}} by dumping of raw sewage, industrial waste and municipal waste into the river. Besides this, illegal activities like washing vessels, animals and oily drums, discharge of unauthorised hazardous waste are also carried {{out along the}} course of this river. Cattle sheds in some areas contribute animal waste. Barrel cleaners, scrap dealers and others dump <b>sludge</b> <b>oil,</b> effluent and garbage in the river. The organic waste, sludge and garbage dumping has reduced the carrying capacity of the river. The water with mixture of sewage and industrial waste is a threat to marine life. The river bed is full of sludge, garbage and vegetation growth like water hyacinth in many parts.|$|E
